openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Jigaysa Smart Hybrid LMS API
  version: 1.0.0
  description: |-
    API for the Smart Hybrid LMS platform.

    **Student modules live:** Auth (incl. OTP + password reset), Courses & enrollment, Free Library, Live Classes, Assessments, Discussions & Community, Notifications, Payments, File Uploads.

    > ⚠️ **Payments run on a MOCK gateway for now.** Checkout, GST invoicing, coupons and access-granting all work end to end, but `POST /orders/{id}/pay/` confirms payment synchronously with a stub — **no real Razorpay/Stripe/PayPal/UPI integration and no money moves yet.** Real gateway + webhook verification is pending.

    > Also pending: refunds, EMI/installments, pay-per-session checkout, corporate/group pricing, referral credits. Recordings (§3.11) and Smart Classroom (§3.7–3.8) are not exposed yet.
